    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gun Shop 3 has its sights set on America’s seemingly insatiable appetite for firearms.  As the Federally licensed Firearms (FFL) Dealer, you will begin your rise to the top with humble beginnings of a spare room in your home or a “less than desirable” location.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Design</strong><br>Life starts now. You’re going to need storage space and safes to securely store your merchandise. As you grow, you will also need to fill your palace of profit with the furnishings needed to conduct your business and appeal to the masses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792350/extras/70eae618f0d198b8319f7cccfb6b4458.poster.avif?t=1743924059\" width=360 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792350/extras/70eae618f0d198b8319f7cccfb6b4458.webm?t=1743924059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792350/extras/70eae618f0d198b8319f7cccfb6b4458.mp4?t=1743924059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build Weaponry</strong><br>Build custom weapons to please your customers. Design normal every day items or unusable beasts. Attach rails to rails scopes to adapters and adapters to points. Adjust this adjust that. Twist it bob it shoot it.   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792350/extras/e2cc4ef1c4eaf3a7acc428b9aac6f012.poster.avif?t=1743924059\" width=360 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792350/extras/e2cc4ef1c4eaf3a7acc428b9aac6f012.webm?t=1743924059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792350/extras/e2cc4ef1c4eaf3a7acc428b9aac6f012.mp4?t=1743924059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Restore</strong><br>Second hand merchandise will likely need some TLC to get into shape to be sold in your store. Use your workbench to clean, revive, and even spruce up your wares to be nice and attractive for your customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792350/extras/c2cc8ee0e10c7f1c4705de0bd3ca1daf.poster.avif?t=1743924059\" width=360 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792350/extras/c2cc8ee0e10c7f1c4705de0bd3ca1daf.webm?t=1743924059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792350/extras/c2cc8ee0e10c7f1c4705de0bd3ca1daf.mp4?t=1743924059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
